speech.p:
asked the President of the Board of Trade (1) what effect the new financial restrictions will have on the number of industrial projects he expects to be started in the county of Durham during the next twelve months;

(2) in view of the new financial restrictions imposed by the Government, what special measures he proposes to take to ensure continuance of his plans to provide in the County of


Durham over 2,500,000 square feet of new factory space, and over 4,000 new jobs.
